em in css (double the size of parent) -> MDN -> https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/font-size 
<p>hjgfiugfiugf<span>dhf</span>udfguyfd</p> 

span{
    font-size : 2.0em; /* It will be double the size of p*/
}

line-heights:

p{
    line-height: 2; /* space between the lines */
}

